53
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,920
graceful and elegant,

54
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,120
gentle and charming.

55
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,190
Among all my weapon spirits,

56
00:04:52,210 --> 00:04:53,240
she's the most obedient.

57
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:55,070
Then I believe this trip with Kai Shan and Lu Chen

58
00:04:55,070 --> 00:04:56,480
will go very smoothly.

59
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,600
They'll indeed have a smooth journey,

60
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:02,160
but it might not be the same for us.

61
00:05:02,250 --> 00:05:03,130
Why is that?

62
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,830
My last weapon spirit

63
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:06,720
is called Xiu.

64
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:07,870
It's of the fire element.

65
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,480
