73
00:06:08,430 --> 00:06:09,630
Come here and look after him.

74
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,800
Yes.

75
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:14,680
Excuse me.

76
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,360
Water.

77
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:18,950
Okay.

78
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,270
Thank you.

79
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,560
Where is this place?

80
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,750
In response to your question, Sir,

81
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,800
this is the City Lord's Mansion in Yandu City.

82
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,270
You're in our young mistress's boudoir.

83
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,070
You got injured,

84
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,800
and our young mistress brought you back.

85
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,950
It's been a few days.

86
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:53,630
Bou-

87
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:55,680
Boudoir?

88
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,040
Yes.

89
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:09,480
Young... Young Mistress.

90
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,000
Young Mistress, please slow down.

91
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,000
These old bones of mine

92
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,000
-can't keep up with you. 
-Hurry up.

93
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,870
Young Mistress. Young Mistress.

94
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:14,630
Come, this way please.

95
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:15,750
Slowly, slowly.

96
00:07:15,770 --> 00:07:16,570
Young Mistress.

97
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:20,800
You mustn't sit.

98
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,920
You mustn't.

99
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,360
Come on.

100
00:07:23,430 --> 00:07:24,240
Come on.

101
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:24,940
Lie down.

102
00:07:33,070 --> 00:07:34,780
Doctor, how is he?

103
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:38,270
His pulse is sluggish and rough,

104
00:07:38,270 --> 00:07:40,190
weak and insufficient,

105
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,430
indicating a condition of exhaustion.

106
00:07:43,010 --> 00:07:45,130
He has chest tightness and shortness of breath,

107
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,920
which is due to the body's defense energy fighting against pathogens,

108
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:49,560
caused by insufficient yang energy.

109
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,070
Additionally, his muscles and bones

110
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,630
were severely injured the other day,

111
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:55,630
and his spleen was also damaged.

112
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,510
It's truly a fundamental injury.

113
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,630
You said the same thing last time.

114
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:03,190
Is he getting better or not?

115
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:07,430
Don't be anxious, Young Mistress.

116
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:10,190
With injuries like these,

117
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:11,950
if he were one of us humans,

118
00:08:11,970 --> 00:08:14,000
he would have died long ago.

119
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:18,720
But Sir here is an immortal of the Youhu Clan.

120
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:21,270
He only needs to rest for half a month...

121
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,200
I mean, three to five months...

122
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:24,540
No, a year or so.

123
00:08:24,570 --> 00:08:27,410
He can fully recover in a year or so.

124
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:28,750
Dr. Zhang.

125
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,440
You're a renowned physician, aren't you?

126
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:33,750
How can your diagnosis be so vague?

127
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:35,240
How long will it actually take?

128
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:37,909
I...

129
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,720
This is also my first time

130
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:43,150
taking the pulse of a Youhu immortal.

131
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,000
In this old man's opinion,

132
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,480
he should have died long ago.

133
00:08:46,550 --> 00:08:47,320
But, but...

134
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,390
He's still alive now, isn't he?

135
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:52,550
If you ask me how many days it will take

136
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:53,840
for him to fully recover,

137
00:08:53,990 --> 00:08:55,990
I really have no idea.

138
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:58,300
Young Mistress. Sir.

139
00:08:58,750 --> 00:08:59,870
This old man takes his leave.

140
00:09:10,390 --> 00:09:11,200
Thanks a lot.

141
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:15,000
I should be the one thanking you.

142
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,750
You got injured while saving me.

143
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,630
Dai.

144
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:30,750
Mr. Tanghua.

145
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,440
This is my younger brother, Zhi Yue.

146
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:36,990
Sir, there's no need for formalities.

147
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,580
Young City Lord Zhi Yue.

148
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:42,790
Thank you for your rescue.

149
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,200
I, Tanghua, am deeply grateful.

150
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:47,120
Sir, you're too kind.

151
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,200
Our two races have always been on good terms.

152
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,550
Besides, you're Dai's friend,

153
00:09:50,790 --> 00:09:52,080
which makes you a friend of our Yandu.

154
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,790
Friends helping each other

155
00:09:53,790 --> 00:09:54,870
is only natural.

156
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:57,750
Sir, you needn't worry.

157
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,630
Just focus on recovering here

158
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:01,600
and make sure to heal properly.

159
00:10:03,510 --> 00:10:04,320
Thank you.

160
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:07,290
Then I won't disturb your rest, Sir.

161
00:10:07,430 --> 00:10:08,310
If there's anything you need,

162
00:10:08,550 --> 00:10:09,550
please don't hesitate to ask.

163
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,320
I'll take my leave now.

164
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:31,840
What's wrong?

165
00:10:35,030 --> 00:10:36,910
Nothing. I'm just curious.

166
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,510
I often hear Father talk about

167
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:39,960
how you were away from home for years because of

168
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,960
this person, Dai.

169
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,580
Now I've finally met him.

170
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:45,270
He's indeed outstanding.

171
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:46,870
You have good taste, Dai.

172
00:10:47,150 --> 00:10:48,360
It's all in the past now.

173
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,480
It's all in the past?

174
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:54,870
Well, never mind.

175
00:10:55,910 --> 00:10:57,120
When will Father come out of seclusion?

176
00:10:57,750 --> 00:10:59,150
I'm not sure about that either.

177
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,030
The immortal medicine you brought back this time

178
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:02,030
is extraordinary, Dai.

179
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:03,670
It might still take some time

180
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:04,670
to absorb its properties.

181
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:06,120
But when the ending draws near,

182
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,200
we'll be notified.

183
00:11:07,590 --> 00:11:09,070
Dai, you need to rest more.

184
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,870
You've visibly lost weight these past few days.

185
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,030
You too.

186
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,480
Well then, Dai, I'll head back now.

187
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,440
No need to see me out.

188
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:23,730
[Ningrui Pavilion]

189
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:10,640
It's all in the past.

190
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:34,080
Chief.

191
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:35,430
We've been on the road for too long.

192
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,200
Everyone is almost at their limit.

193
00:12:37,510 --> 00:12:38,360
How about we find a place

194
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,150
to rest and recuperate?

195
00:12:39,670 --> 00:12:41,510
There's a water source 10 miles to the east.

196
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,840
Let's go rest there.

197
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:43,960
Yes.

198
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,150
Why are you staring at me?

199
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,240
Since you found out

200
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,630
I'm the Mute Lady of Wu Mountain,

201
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:11,080
you've always wanted to drive me away.

202
00:13:11,660 --> 00:13:12,900
Why don't you want to drive me away now?

203
00:13:13,530 --> 00:13:15,170
You saved me again in my sea of consciousness.

204
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:17,480
How could I have the heart to drive you away now?

205
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:20,870
But I'd saved you before that, too.

206
00:13:21,890 --> 00:13:22,720
Then leave.

207
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,150
I'm driving you away.

208
00:13:32,750 --> 00:13:33,960
I want to ask you a question.

209
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,910
Earlier, in your sea of consciousness,

210
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:40,960
I saw myself.

211
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,200
You pictured me as

212
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,510
a witch,

213
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:45,530
foolishly guarding the door for you.

214
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:47,240
That demon said

215
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:49,390
this means you both guard against me

216
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:50,600
and trust me.

217
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,720
So, do you really guard against me

218
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,960
or trust me?

219
00:13:58,910 --> 00:13:59,720
Also,

220
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:01,480
your dreams

221
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,870
get scarier with each layer.

222
00:14:05,510 --> 00:14:06,750
So what's in your ninth layer

223
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:07,600
of dreams?

224
00:14:07,870 --> 00:14:08,670
Ji Tanyin.

225
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,320
Why does the War Demon

226
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,630
have your birth date and time

227
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:14,200
and is able to possess you?

228
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:17,710
I... I don't know either.

229
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,000
Then are you willing to let me enter

230
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,150
your sea of consciousness?

231
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,510
In other words,

232
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,030
are you willing to let me know

233
00:14:23,030 --> 00:14:24,510
the secrets in your heart?

234
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:31,430
Since you're not willing yourself,

235
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,080
what right do you have

236
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,600
to know everything about me?

237
00:14:38,270 --> 00:14:39,270
Let me give you a piece of advice.

238
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:40,910
Don't try to know

239
00:14:40,910 --> 00:14:42,440
everything about anyone.

240
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:44,310
You'll be disappointed.

241
00:15:31,910 --> 00:15:32,690
Chief.

242
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,770
I have a question to ask.

243
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:40,550
I don't understand.

244
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,480
I saw it clearly at that time,

245
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:45,960
Chief, that you clearly had the chance

246
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,840
to plunge the dagger into his heart,

247
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,150
but you held back.

248
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,600
Because I saw his eyes.

249
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:57,560
Those were the eyes of a demon.

250
00:15:58,380 --> 00:15:59,490
The eyes of a demon?

251
00:16:00,790 --> 00:16:01,750
How is that possible?

252
00:16:02,150 --> 00:16:03,120
It's impossible indeed.

253
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:05,480
He is the High Priest of the Youhu Clan,

254
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:07,270
and he possesses the Divine Left Hand.

255
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:10,510
Why would he have the eyes of a demon?

256
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:33,790
Where are you going?

257
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:34,840
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

258
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:35,670
Come with me.

259
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:36,670
Let go of me!

260
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,240
My mother is still in Gushan.

261
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,630
I need to go back and find her.

262
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:40,840
You won't find her.

263
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:41,550
I can!

264
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:43,550
Can't you just listen to me?

265
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:44,730
I won't!

266
00:16:44,760 --> 00:16:45,410
You-

267
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:55,270
Chief.

268
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:02,400
How old is your mother?

269
00:17:05,380 --> 00:17:06,339
Don't you know?

270
00:17:07,589 --> 00:17:09,000
She must not be young anymore.

271
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,710
Ming Zhang was right.

272
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:12,200
You won't find her.

273
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,270
Why?

274
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:14,569
She's already dead.

275
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:15,560
That's impossible!

276
00:17:17,220 --> 00:17:18,910
Our clan has the blood of the divine race.

277
00:17:19,069 --> 00:17:20,109
We have long lifespans.

278
00:17:20,270 --> 00:17:21,440
How could she have died?

279
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:23,200
According to our clan's rules,

280
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:25,109
men protect the clan and kill enemies

281
00:17:25,109 --> 00:17:26,240
until their last breath,

282
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:27,849
while women bear offspring

283
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,160
also until their last breath.

284
00:17:29,550 --> 00:17:31,510
Our clan's constitution is different from that of the human race.

285
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,400
Childbirth damages the mother's body

